nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A tall, confident blonde woman with long flowing hair, glowing turquoise earrings, and cyberpunk tattoos stands beside a glossy red Ferrari Testarossa, one hand on the open door, the other on the roof, her black latex mini dress traced with neon-blue circuitry patterns and the bold “COMFY UI” logo shimmering under the city lights. She turns her gaze toward the camera, lips curling into a playful smile before giving a quick, teasing wink. The golden sunset blends with magenta and cyan neon from the futuristic coastal skyline, casting shimmering reflections across wet pavement and rolling waves. Captured with a 50mm lens in ultra-high resolution on a RED V-Raptor HDR setup, the camera orbits slowly around the Ferrari, gliding from the prancing horse emblem past her elegant figure to frame her face in shallow depth of field. She slides into the driver’s seat, shuts the door, and the engine erupts with a deep, aggressive roar. Tires shriek as the Ferrari launches fast forward, spinning the rear wheels and sending thick, swirling clouds of white smoke cascading into the neon-lit street. The orbiting shot continues seamlessly into a dynamic follow, the smoke catching bursts of pink, blue, and gold light, merging retro sports car elegance with raw cyberpunk power.
